//|   S        -  clusterizer state, initialized by                  |
//|               ClusterizerCreate()                                |
//|   Seed     -  seed:                                              |
//|               * positive values = use deterministic seed for each|
//|                 run of algorithms which depend on random         |
//|                 initialization                                   |
