//| Use AutoGKSingular in such cases.                                |
//| INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                |
//|     A, B    -   interval boundaries (A<B, A=B or A>B)            |
//| OUTPUT PARAMETERS                                                |
//|     State   -   structure which stores algorithm state           |
//| SEE ALSO                                                         |
//|     AutoGKSmoothW, AutoGKSingular, AutoGKResults.                |
//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
