//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
//| Conversion from barycentric representation to Chebyshev basis.   |
//| This function has O(N^2) complexity.                             |
//| INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                |
//|     P   -   polynomial in barycentric form                       |
