//| This function fits model of the form                             |
//|      F(x|A,B,C,D) = D+(A-D)/(1+Power(x/C,B))   (4PL model)       |
//| or                                                               |
//|      F(x|A,B,C,D,G) = D+(A-D)/Power(1+Power(x/C,B),G)(5PL model) |
//| Here:                                                            |
//|   * A, D         -  unconstrained                                |
