//| matrices can find element in O(1) time, while CRS matrices need  |
//| O(log(RS)) time, where RS is an number of non-zero elements in a |
//| row.                                                             |
//| INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                |
//|   S     -  sparse M*N matrix                                     |
