//|    optimizer.                                                    |
//|                   |         USER PASSED TO MinCGOptimize()       |
//|    CREATED WITH   |  function only   |  function and gradient    |
//|    ------------------------------------------------------------  |
//|    MinCGCreateF() |     work                FAIL                 |
//|    MinCGCreate()  |     FAIL                work                 |
