//|             -                                                    |
//|            | |                                                   |
//|            |           dt                                        |
//| K(m)  =    |    ------------------                               |
//|            |                   2                                 |
//|          | |    sqrt( 1 - m sin t )                              |
//|           -                                                      |
//|            0                                                     |
//| using the approximation                                          |
//|     P(x)  -  log x Q(x).                                         |
//| ACCURACY:                                                        |
//|                      Relative error:                             |
//| arithmetic   domain     # trials      peak         rms           |
//|    IEEE       0,1        30000       2.5e-16     6.8e-17         |
