//| from 0 to x of the Poisson density is equal to the               |
//| given probability y.                                             |
//| This is accomplished using the inverse gamma integral            |
//| function and the relation                                        |
//|    m = igami( k+1, y ).                                          |
//| ACCURACY:                                                        |
//| See inverse incomplete gamma function                            |
//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
